msgid "Provides redstone power when pushed"
msgstr "Dostarcza energię czerwienitową gdy naciśnięta"

msgid "Pushable by players, mobs and objects"
msgstr "Możliwa do naciśnięcia przez graczy, moby i obiekty"

msgid "Pushable by players and mobs"
msgstr "Możliwa do naciśnięcia przez graczy i moby"

msgid "Pushable by mobs"
msgstr "Możliwa do naciśnięcia przez moby"

msgid "Pushable by players"
msgstr "Możliwa do naciśnięcia przez graczy"

msgid "Stone Pressure Plate"
msgstr "Kamienna płyta naciskowa"

msgid "A stone pressure plate is a redstone component which supplies its surrounding blocks with redstone power while a player or mob stands on top of it. It is not triggered by anything else."
msgstr "Kamienna płyta naciskowa jest mechanizmem czerwienitowym, która zasila otaczające bloki energią czerwienitową gdy gracz lub mob na niej stoi. Nie jest aktywowana niczym innym."

msgid "Polished Blackstone Pressure Plate"
msgstr ""

msgid "A polished blackstone pressure plate is a redstone component which supplies its surrounding blocks with redstone power while a player or mob stands on top of it. It is not triggered by anything else."
msgstr ""

msgid "Light Weighted Pressure Plate"
msgstr ""

msgid "A heavy weighted pressure plate is a redstone component which supplies its surrounding blocks with one redstone power for every movable object (including dropped items, players and mobs) that rests on top of it."
msgstr ""

msgid "Heavy Weighted Pressure Plate"
msgstr ""

msgid "A heavy weighted pressure plate is a redstone component which supplies its surrounding blocks with one redstone power for every 10 movable objects (including dropped items, players and mobs) that rest on top of it."
msgstr ""
